title: Ep. #5 | PARK BOM, GRAY, and NU'EST
description:
CONTEST WINNERS ANNOUNCED! Also, Eric talks about PARK BOM’s “4:44 ft. Wheein (Mamamoo)”, GRAY’s “TMI”, NU’EST’s “Bet Bet”, and adds in a few noteworthy personal recs. Eric also talks about his new song “Runaway” that drops this week on May 8th.


We hope you enjoy the show! As always, if you enjoy this podcast, make sure to subscribe and leave us a comment / rating on iTunes, Spotify, Soundcloud and YouTube. It helps us tremendously :).


Thank you for listening, Daebak Show family!


Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios


Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !
